title: confidence, discipline + life advice with madi prewett
itunes:title: confidence, discipline + life advice with madi prewett
description:
Brooke and Danielle sit down with Madison Prewett to share some learnings from her new book, Made for This Moment!  The gals discuss best tips for when you aren’t feeling yourself, how to stay motivated, life post-Bachelor, and so much more!  Brooke and Danielle also catch up on what’s happening in their lives this holiday season.  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories.
